# Cloudflare Pages routing
# First-match-wins. Real asset misses 404 cleanly instead of being masked as
# the SPA shell (text/html), which previously broke module loading.
# Navigation requests still fall back to the SPA shell.
/*.js     /404-asset    404
/*.mjs    /404-asset    404
/*.css    /404-asset    404
/*.map    /404-asset    404
/*        /index.html   200
